sequenceDiagram
    participant Platform
    participant Process as "MCP Server Process"
    participant Transport as "StdioServerTransport"
    participant Server as "MCP Server Instance"
    participant Client as "AutoMemClient"
    
    Platform->>Process: Spawn with stdio
    Process->>Process: Detect server mode<br/>(no CLI args)
    Process->>Process: Redirect console.log<br/>to stderr
    Process->>Process: Load .env quietly<br/>(DOTENV_CONFIG_QUIET)
    Process->>Transport: Create stdio transport
    Process->>Server: Initialize with tools[]
    Server->>Transport: Connect via transport.start()
    
    loop Request/Response Cycle
        Platform->>Transport: JSON-RPC request via stdin
        Transport->>Server: Parse & route request
        Server->>Server: Match CallToolRequestSchema
        Server->>Client: Call AutoMemClient method
        Client->>Client: HTTP request with retry
        Client-->>Server: Return response/error
        Server->>Transport: Format JSON-RPC response
        Transport->>Platform: Write to stdout
    end
    
    Platform->>Process: Close stdin (EOF)
    Transport->>Transport: Detect EPIPE/ECONNRESET
    Process->>Process: Exit gracefully